::: {#cell-fig-timeline .cell}

```{.r .cell-code .hidden}
set.seed(1000)
births_df <- starwars |> 
  drop_na(birth_year) |> 
  slice_sample(n = 8) 

births_df |> 
  ggplot(aes(birth_year, !is.na(birth_year))) +
  geom_point() +
  labs(x = "Year", y = "Birth") +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(axis.text.y = element_blank(),
        axis.ticks.y = element_blank()) 
```

